        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "酸涩的情绪一下子蔓延开来，她能够清晰地感受到心脏被什么紧紧攥住的感觉。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 67,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "瑟瑞斯悠游",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc32ep8_girl013_05",
        "zh_CN": "（想要记住他……）",
